properties.Name: GeneralMaterialsBudget
properties.Description:
The Indirect Materials Budget details the cost items that are not related to a specific product or service but must be purchased to support the overall or combined operations of the organization.

Theses materials are not directly tracked or identified with a specific product or service.

Columns.Name: GeneralMaterialsBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a General Materials Budget.

Columns.Name: GeneralMaterialsBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a General Materials Budget Version.

Columns.Name: GeneralOperatingBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a General Operating Budget.

Columns.Name: GeneralOperatingBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a General Operating Budget Version.

Columns.Name: BudgetedMaterialsCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The budgeted/planned Materials costs for the associated period general budget.

Columns.Name: ActualMaterialsCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The actual Indirect Materials costs for the associated period general budget.
